Usage: createRuler [-help] {{-center {x y} -radius <float>} | -coordinates {x1 y1 x2 y2 ...}}

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
-center {x y}                      # The Center Location (point, optional)
-coordinates {x1 y1 x2 y2 ...}     # The beginning and ending coordinates for
                                   # the ruler line segments (values are in
                                   # microns) (point_list, optional)
-radius <float>                    # radius of cricle (float, optional)